               kpred:description  "Route web integrations through a self-hosted n8n instance (open-source automation, no SaaS). The clean division of labour: the app stays static/offline-first and owns the VISUAL building; n8n owns the web side-effects (email, sheets, tickets, monitoring). settings.n8nBaseUrl (Settings → Integrations) points at the instance." ;
               kpred:has-workflow  kb:n8n-sync-hub ;
